title: The Weirdest One Yet?
description: TODAY'S MYSTERY VIDEO -   IN1 Multi Tool Case for iPhone -   I've looked at many strange iPhone cases over the years but the IN1 multi tool case may be the weirdest yet. It combines tools in a similar fashion to a swiss army knife, except in this case they live inside a phone case. The model featured here works with the iPhone 6, iPhone 6 Plus, iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus.  FOLLOW ME IN THESE PLACES FOR UPDATES Twitter -  Facebook -  Instagram -  Google Plus -
